docker build -t ecdsa-backend .
docker run -p 8000:8000 ecdsa-backend


### How to use logging config inside your attack scripts
from logging_config import logger

logger.info("Starting replay attack simulation…")


######

⭐ F. Connecting the React UI

Inside your Web UI button:
    await fetch("http://localhost:8000/attack/weak-k");

For logs (WebSocket):
    const ws = new WebSocket("ws://localhost:8000/ws/logs");
    ws.onmessage = (e) => setLogs(prev => [...prev, e.data]);


