###
Inside webUI, buttons like:

    Run Replay Attack
    Run Weak‑k Attack
    Run Signature Forgery
    Run MITM Attack
    Run Malleability Attack

But they don’t do anything until they call a backend.

➡ Meaning:
You must add a backend API that the buttons talk to.

Where logs go
✔ To console
✔ To logs/attack_simulation.log
✔ To the web UI (when we wire WebSocket)


